The 37th European Club Cup is a 7-round Swiss tournament taking place from 3–9 October 2022 in Mayrhofen, Austria.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.eccc2022.at
